    <h3> reqT &ndash; a scalable requirements tool </h3>
    <p> reqT is a <b>free</b>, <b>flexible</b> and <b>scalable</b> requirements engineering tool <br/> for 
    system analysts, developers and software engineering students. </p>

    <p> With reqT you can ... 
      <ul>
        <li> model, analyse, visualize and prioritize requirements  </li>
        <li> combine natural language with formal structure </li>
        <li> flexibly mix abstraction levels and modelling approaches
        <li> integrate requirements and test specification </li>
        <li> export and import models via open formats  </li>
        <li> manipulate models with powerful Scala scripts  </li>
        <li> allocate requirements to releases with constraint solving </li>
      </ul>
    </p> 
    
